### Main Components Used

* Microcontroller (Arduino or similar)
* Real Time Clock (RTC) module
* GSM module
* Voice playback module
* Buzzer
* Push buttons (for schedule setting)
* LED indicators (pill slot indication)
* Load cell weight sensor
